snippet.title: Twisted Metal (PS1) Gameplay
snippet.description:
A quick playthrough of Sweet Tooth's story in Twisted Metal. The cheats I used here was Infinite ammo, Invinvcibility, Unlimited turbo, and Rapid fire.
